{"tid":1679084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［大圍］小心大圍源記餐廳","createTime":"2019-10-28T03:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T04:15:39.000Z","uid":152426,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b87bb06ebecd9ed9a80c36dc32247ad97a42800c","tid":1679084,"uid":152426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"事源我岩岩出左大圍食晏，我著住普通衫同戴住個醫生口罩入左源記<br />\n有個阿叔（員工）過黎幫我落單個陣，即係望住我話「哇，口罩黨啊」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我話「係咪病戴口罩都唔得？」<br />\n佢keep住講口罩黨講左幾次<br />\n我就話「咁以家係咪唔歡迎我？」<br />\n佢無出聲，但係就好不屑咁係到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃藍商店無話大圍源記係藍定黃<br />\n但有會講d咁既野既藍伙記 大圍手足都係小心d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kFW3yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kFW3yZ.jpg&h=e766465d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2UBrGkS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2UBrGkS.png&h=75d18d65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cef4aa8667bf453c4c0a0abb043b9a12d9316bf0","tid":1679084,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e5eab301f245d6103ae787f5f8a5372d515b491a","tid":1679084,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"又貴又難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878e658558d2912916d3053760920ce687716fc8","tid":1679084,"uid":143151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets